00101         calvinCel.GetAlgorithmParameters(algParams);

00104                 if (ii != algParams.begin())

00176 /*
00177  */
00178 std::wstring CalvinCELDataAdapter::GetDatHeader()
00179 {
00180         std::wstring datHeader;
00181 
00182         //GenDataHdrVectorIt begin, end; 
00183         GenericDataHeader* gdh = calvinCel.GetFileHeader()->GetGenericDataHdr()->FindParent(SCAN_ACQUISITION_DATA_TYPE);
00184         if (gdh)
00185         {
00186                 // found the right header, now look for the parameter
00187                 ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00188                 if (gdh->FindNameValParam(DAT_HEADER_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00189                 {
00190                         if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::TextType)
00191                                 datHeader = nvt.GetValueText();
00192                 }
00193                 else if (gdh->FindNameValParam(PARTIAL_DAT_HEADER_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00194                 {
00195                         if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::TextType)
00196                         {
00197                                 std::wstring partialDatHeader = nvt.GetValueText();
00198 
00199                                 u_int16_t min = 0;
00200                                 u_int16_t max = 0;
00201 
00202                                 // Find the max and min parameters and append to the string.
00203                                 if (gdh->FindNameValParam(MAX_PIXEL_INTENSITY_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00204                                 {
00205                                         if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type)
00206                                                 max = nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00207                                 }
00208 
00209                                 if (gdh->FindNameValParam(MIN_PIXEL_INTENSITY_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00210                                 {
00211                                         if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type)
00212                                                 min = nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00213                                 }
00214 
00215                                 wchar_t buf[30]=L"";
00216                                 FormatString2(buf, 30, L"[%d..%d]", min, max);
00217                                 datHeader = buf;
00218                                 datHeader += partialDatHeader;
00219                         }
00220                 }
00221         }
00222         return datHeader;
00223 }

00225 /*
00226  */
00227 int CalvinCELDataAdapter::GetCellMargin()
00228 {
00229         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00230         if (calvinCel.FindAlgorithmParameter(CELLMARGIN_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00231         {
00232                 switch(nvt.GetParameterType())
00233                 {
00234                 case ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type:
00235                         return nvt.GetValueInt32();
00236                         break;
00237                 case ParameterNameValueType::Int16Type:
00238                         return (int)nvt.GetValueInt16();
00239                         break;
00240                 case ParameterNameValueType::Int8Type:
00241                         return (int)nvt.GetValueInt8();
00242                         break;
00243                 case ParameterNameValueType::UInt32Type:
00244                         return (int)nvt.GetValueUInt32();
00245                         break;
00246                 case ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type:
00247                         return (int)nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00248                         break;
00249                 case ParameterNameValueType::UInt8Type:
00250                         return (int)nvt.GetValueUInt8();
00251                         break;
00252                 case ParameterNameValueType::AsciiType:
00253                         return (int)atoi(nvt.GetValueAscii().c_str());
00254                 default:
00255                         return 0;
00256                         break;
00257                 }
00258         }
00259         else
00260         {
00261                 return 0;
00262         }
00263 }
